    "body": "### Problem\r\n\r\nRefresh only work on current buffer, but I want to refesh code lens for all buffers once.\r\n![image](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/32760059/2bb42a54-a23c-43ea-a352-c1b009c95867)\r\n![image](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/32760059/ceb29091-8eee-4a77-86db-1d78514bfb7a)\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n```\r\nrefresh({client_id}, {bufnr})                         *vim.lsp.codelens.refresh()*\r\n    Refresh the lenses\r\n\r\n    Parameters: ~\r\n      • {client_id}  (`integer?`) filter by client_id. All clients if nil\r\n      • {bufnr}      (`integer?`) filter by buffer. All buffers if nil\r\n```",
